{"tid":620976,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"人死後係永遠黑暗, 還是真係有意識繼續長存?","createTime":"2018-04-08T02:11:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T11:41:08.000Z","uid":180184,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b3d1fe7f34850dd06ea10d735296d51b5b08c3","tid":620976,"uid":180184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T02:11:37.000Z","msg":"睇左一D 書同網站, 唔同國家都有好多人做實驗.<br />\n例如有人許諾比一個即將要處死既海盜家人利益, 要身體極強項既海盜被砍頭身分離後聽到佢呼喚時嘗試眨眼.<br />\n海盜被處決, 身首異處後, 醫生呼喚佢, 海盜真係可以係頭身分離既情況下貶左一下眼, 然後再呼喚就無反應.<br />\n咁樣嘗試證明意識最後會係腦袋而非身體?<br />\n<br />\n又有實驗測量出靈魂重35公克，人死後會靈魂離體<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/science/2b5boz.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fscience%2F2b5boz.html&d=6sBp%2F%2FOpXbirerEnLVeCClKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=31bd6b23\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/science/2b5boz.html</a><br />\n<br />\n然後又睇左一D 瀕死經驗既研究(超心理學?)<br />\n係講有好多人係腦死亡甚至停左心跳呼吸後突然復甦,同時可以表達當時見到既野.<br />\n<br />\n美國哈佛大學博士、知名神經外科醫生埃本&bull;亞歷山大發表了《天堂的證據》一書中的片段，文中詳細精確地描述了自己的瀕死體驗<br />\n<br />\n亞歷山大以前並不相信瀕死體驗，他接受過科學教育，追隨父親的道路成了一名神經外科醫生，還在哈佛醫學院等高校授課。但後來的一次親身經歷徹底改變了他的想法。<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2012/10/16/a781072.html.-%E5%93%88%E4%BD%9B%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B77%E5%A4%A9%E7%80%95%E6%AD%BB%E9%AB%94%E9%A9%97--%E8%A9%B3%E8%BF%B0%E3%80%8C%E5%A4%A9%E5%A0%82%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85%E3%80%8D.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fxtr%2Fb5%2F2012%2F10%2F16%2Fa781072.html.-%25E5%2593%2588%25E4%25BD%259B%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2598%258F%25E8%25BF%25B77%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%2580%2595%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E9%25AB%2594%25E9%25A9%2597--%25E8%25A9%25B3%25E8%25BF%25B0%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%25A0%2582%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%2597%2585%25E3%2580%258D.html&d=6sBp%2F%2FOpXbirerEnLVeCClKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=d6da03f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2012/10/16/a781072.html.-%E5%93%88%E4%BD%9B%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B77%E5%A4%A9%E7%80%95%E6%AD%BB%E9%AB%94%E9%A9%97--%E8%A9%B3%E8%BF%B0%E3%80%8C%E5%A4%A9%E5%A0%82%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85%E3%80%8D.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國著名心理學家雷蒙德&middot;A&middot;穆迪博士，在研究過150個瀕死體驗者(經歷過「臨床死亡」後復生的人)的案例之後，正在試圖為人們揭開死亡真相。<br />\n在這些人「瀕死體驗」的陳述中，存在著不可忽視的相似性&mdash;&mdash;把它們大體歸納為14條<br />\n靈魂脫體<br />\n時間消失<br />\n體驗愉悅<br />\n感官靈敏<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://read01.com/PdOya.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2FPdOya.html&d=6sBp%2F%2FOpXbirerEnLVeCClKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=2726de94\" target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/PdOya.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n植物人昏迷12年驚醒：「手術、一切我都有意識..卻只能躺著..」<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"http://health663.blogspot.hk/2017/10/12.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhealth663.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F10%2F12.html&d=6sBp%2F%2FOpXbirerEnLVeCClKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=6374d86b\" target=\"_blank\">http://health663.blogspot.hk/2017/10/12.html</a>"},{"pid":"0cc959d50d6e7672547c6b3dcca8e9a4898992da","tid":620976,"uid":28641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T02:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106ed31834ec197bcfbafb358a977c6a71961936","tid":620976,"uid":15208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T02:25:34.000Z","msg":"重要咩？"},{"pid":"f7c1cac24af1c42122b4d6484807be24afa3c56b","tid":620976,"uid":180184,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"106ed31834ec197bcfbafb358a977c6a71961936","tid":620976,"uid":15208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T02:25:34.000Z","msg":"重要咩？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T02:26:15.000Z","msg":"對於有親人去世既人黎講,我覺得幾重要架.."},{"pid":"41bebaec205d18371617554c2236bc300cad2b8c","tid":620976,"uid":38548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f7c1cac24af1c42122b4d6484807be24afa3c56b","tid":620976,"uid":180184,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"106ed31834ec197bcfbafb358a977c6a71961936","tid":620976,"uid":